Package com.bteam.common.models

Class LobbyModel

java.lang.Object
com.bteam.common.models.LobbyModel
public class LobbyModel extends Object
This class represents the game lobby.

A lobby, consisting of its name, ID, Players, Player Limit and the current LobbyModel.GameState
